<p>I want to be able to toggle the 'data-close-any' attribute for the metro accordion.</p>  <p>Here is the jQuery, which is working in as much as it is changing the attribute value, but the functionality is not changing at all.</p>  <pre><code>$('#toggleAccordionCloseAny').click(function () {             if ($('input#toggleAccordionCloseAny').is(':checked')) {                 $('.accordion').attr("data-close-any", true);             }             else {                 $('.accordion').removeAttr('data-close-any');             }         }); </code></pre>  <p>What else do I need to do to get this functionality working?</p>